                                    <h2 class="mt-20 mb-20"> Customizing the grid<a href="" id="Customizing-the-grid"
                                            class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h2>
                                    <p>The default grid classes can be entirely altered using theÂ built-in grid Sass variables and maps. Alter the container widths, media query dimensions, and tier count before recompiling.</p>
                                    <h3 class="mt-20 mb-20">Columns and gutters <a href="" id="Columns-and-gutters"
                                            class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a> </h3>
                                    <p>The number of grid columns can be modified via Sass variables. <code
                                            class="code_bg">$grid-columns</code> is used to generate the widths (in
                                        percent) of each individual column while <code
                                            class="code_bg">$grid-gutter-width</code> sets the width for the column
                                        gutters.</p>
