                                            <i class="fa fa-copy" id="iconCopied21"></i>
                                        </button>
                                        <pre id="copyText21"><code>$grid-columns: 12 !default;
$grid-gutter-width: 1.5rem !default;
$grid-row-columns: 6 !default;</code></pre>
                                    </div>
                                    <!-- code end -->
                                    <h3>Grid tiers <a href="" id="Grid-tiers" class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h3>
                                    <p>Beyond the actual columns, chooseÂ how many grid layers there are. Update the <code>$grid-breakpoints</code> and <code>$container-max-widths</code> to something like this if there is only a need ofÂ four grid tiers:</p>
